                    "オペレーターは体力が十分なため、サポートできません",
                    "Selected operator is at max mood",
                    "No recovery required",
                    "干员心情已满",
                    "幹員心情已滿",
                    "无法使用助力",
                    "無法使用助力"
                ]
            }
        },
        "pre_delay": 0,
        "post_delay": 0,
        "rate_limit": 0,
        "next": [
            "RecoveryEmotionExitView2ToView1"
        ],
        "focus": {
            "Node.PipelineNode.Failed": "$task.DijiangRewards.focus.recovery_emotion_full_prompt_failed"
        }
    },
    "RecoveryEmotionView2In": {
        "desc": "[恢复心情·状态] 已打开「选择待恢复心情的干员」界面，开始选择待恢复心情的干员",
